---
title: Prawns, Tofu & Sweet Chilli Veggie Stir-Fry with Egg Noodles & Crushed Peanuts
description: We’re stirring and frying these soft little tofu cubes tonight in our favourite sweet soy seasoning. Toss them through oodles of egg noodles with veggies and a too-good-to-be-true sweet chilli stir fry sauce, with a sprinkling of peanuts on top for crunch. It’s a gold star from us!

